net.tridentsdk.plugin.annotation

Annotation Type IgnoreRegistration


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={METHOD,TYPE})
public @interface IgnoreRegistration
    Marks a class which registration should exclude so the user may register manually

    Do not use the annotation in order to acquire the instance of a registered class. You may use the Plugin.listenerBy(Class) to find an instance of a listener and Plugin.commandBy(Class) to find an instance of a command

    Since:
    0.3-alpha-DP
    Author:
    The TridentSDK Team
